OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1782370082
OL,3,CWoman, 72, who died after stabbing
OL,4,Cnamed in murder investigation
OL,6,FA woman found dead at a property in
OL,7,Fsouth Derbyshire has been named as 72-
OL,8,Fyear-old Joan Hardy.
OL,10,FDerbyshire Police were called to
OL,11,Freports that a woman had been found
OL,12,Fwith stab wounds at a house in
OL,13,FSwadlincote on Sunday 21 June.
OL,15,FJoan Hardy was pronounced dead at the
OL,16,Fscene, and her family have been made
OL,17,Faware by police, who said they are
OL,18,Fbeing supported by specialist officers.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
