FL,348,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1782370082
OL,3,CWoman, 72, who died after stabbing
OL,4,Cnamed in murder investigation
OL,6,FA 52-year-old man has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder and remains in
OL,8,Fpolice custody.
OL,10,FA scene remains at the house and is
OL,11,Fexpected to be in place for a number
OL,12,Fof days, while officers make house
OL,13,Fcalls and review CCTV.
OL,15,FDerbyshire Police said it wants to
OL,16,Fhear from anyone who has CCTV, Ring
OL,17,Fdoorbell or dash cam footage which
OL,18,Fcovers The Crest in Linton between
OL,19,F12.01am on Saturday 20 June, and 3pm
OL,20,Fon Sunday 21 June.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,348,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1782370082
OL,3,CWoman, 72, who died after stabbing
OL,4,Cnamed in murder investigation
OL,6,FOn Monday, Detective Inspector Tony
OL,7,FOwen, from the East Midlands Special
OL,8,FOperations Unit, who is leading the
OL,9,Finvestigation, said: "Members of the
OL,10,Fpublic can expect to see an increased
OL,11,Fpolice presence in the area while we
OL,12,Fcarry out our enquiries.
OL,14,F"We are aware that this may cause some
OL,15,Fconcern in the community, but I would
OL,16,Flike to reassure residents that this
OL,17,Fis believed to be an isolated incident.
OL,19,F"If you have any concerns or would
OL,20,Flike to pass on any information,
OL,21,Fplease feel free to approach officers."
OL,26,@qD@VOUvD@AOU{D@AOU}D@gO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
