PN,34704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1782370082
OL,3,CWoman, 72, who died after stabbing
OL,4,Cnamed in murder investigation
OL,6,FAs part of the investigation, police
OL,7,Fare appealing for anyone with
OL,8,Finformation to come forward.
OL,10,FOfficers are keen to hear from anyone
OL,11,Fwith CCTV, Ring doorbell or dash cam
OL,12,Ffootage which covers The Crest between
OL,13,F12.01am on Saturday (20 June) and 3pm
OL,14,Fon Sunday (21 June).
OL,16,FA portal has been set up where people
OL,17,Fcan send information directly to the
OL,18,Fpolice via this link.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
